T02D3654:263b-1: manydzu gho sha ma h'a r'a dza l'i la s'a dha nam /
T02D3654:263b-3: rgyal bo chen po rol pa'i 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3654:263b-4: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3654:263b-5: bcom ldan 'das 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi sgrub thabs brjod par bya ste /
T02D3654:263b-6: sa bon drug pa'i lnga pa la dbyangs kyi yi ge lnga pas brgyan pa /
T02D3654:263b-8: sa bon de nyid las byung ba'i mgon po 'jam pa'i dbyangs gzhon nu'i cha lugs can /
T02D3654:263b-9: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02D3654:263b-11: phyag g-yon na autpa la sngon po bsnams pa /
T02D3654:263b-12: phyag g-yas pa rol bas seng ge'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
T02D3654:263b-13: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan par bdag nyid bsams la /
T02D3654:263b-14: lag pa gnyis thal mo khong stong du byas la /
T02D3654:263b-15: mdzub mo gnyis kyis srin lag gnyis kyi sen mo
T02D3654:263b-16: mnan te bzhag pa ni autpa la kha bye ba'i
T02D3654:263b-17: phyag rgya ste / 'dis snying ga dang /
T02D3654:263b-19: lkog ma dang spyi bor gtugs par bya'o //
T02D3654:263b-20: aom w'a g'i shva ri mum /
